1
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,400
The number you have dialed

2
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,130
cannot be reached at this time.

3
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,880
Please try again later.

4
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,810
Good morning, brother.

5
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,600
Good morning, Uncle Lu.

6
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,600
Morning, sister.

7
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,400
Morning, Xia.

8
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,159
Fan,

9
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:44,880
not much work lately?

10
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:47,120
It's rare to see you eating at home.

11
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,920
I've been exhausted.

12
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:55,680
I just wanted to have a meal at home.

13
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,760
Are you cold, Xia?

14
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:01,760
You're wearing a coat at home.

15
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,680
I caught a cold.

16
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,140
I'm not feeling very well.

17
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,330
Remember to take medicine.

18
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,200
Brother,

19
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:11,880
come a bit closer.

20
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:21,080
Li, a bit higher on your side.

21
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:24,480
You, a bit higher.

22
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:26,880
Lift it up.

23
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:27,840
Up.

24
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:29,120
Be careful.

25
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,360
Don't drop it.

26
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,770
Come on, a bit higher on the right side.

27
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:35,960
That's right. No, too much.

28
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:36,680
A bit lower.

29
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:40,440
Congratulations, Ms. Su.

30
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:43,200
Oh, congratulations, Mrs. Lu.

31
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,060
Now that everyone is here,

32
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,610
I have something to say.

33
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:09,320
Dong and I have decided

34
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:11,620
to hold the wedding next week.

35
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:17,040
I don't agree!

36
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:24,970
You don't agree?

37
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:28,080
We've sent the invitations.

38
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:30,440
You're the heir to the Lu family.

39
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:32,840
Fan, listen,

40
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:34,320
I'll drag you there

41
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,780
even if I have to tie you up.

42
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,480
By the way,

43
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:51,800
I prepared a wedding gift for you.

44
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:53,560
You'll see it at the wedding.

45
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,860
That's so thoughtful of you, Xia.

46
00:07:59,880 --> 00:08:00,560
Let's eat.

47
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,320
Jiang Dahai.

48
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,960
Jiang Dahai,

49
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,080
where are you?

50
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,850
Why do you want to see me?

51
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:29,940
Of course because I have something
to discuss with you.

52
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,400
Ms. Su.

53
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:39,320
It's so hot today,

54
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:42,880
and you've been standing here
for a long time.

55
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,640
I'm worried about you.

56
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,160
Actually, fish

57
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:51,480
also have their hidden pains

58
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:54,440
just like you do, Ms. Su.

59
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,520
I understand.

60
00:08:56,880 --> 00:08:59,480
And so does Master Lu,

61
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,400
right?

62
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,120
I understand.

63
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,720
After all, my sister and I have to

64
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,880
rely on others.

65
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:14,360
Young Master Lu is young and impetuous.

66
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:16,640
He needs time to think it through.

67
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,280
It's totally normal.

68
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:19,840
Ms. Su,

69
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:23,120
why so obsessed about a title?

70
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:25,920
Master Lu has done so much

71
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:27,800
for you and Xia.

72
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:31,440
Do you know how many people dream of

73
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:34,040
living a stable
and wealthy life like this?

74
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:36,480
You should be grateful.

75
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:39,680
Butler Jiang,

76
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:44,560
do you really think I’m enduring all this

77
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:46,040
just for a big mansion

78
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:47,720
and a wealthy life?

79
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,960
You're wrong.

80
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,100
I'm doing this for Xia.

81
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,240
I only hope she can

82
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,920
no longer live in fear.

83
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,280
But now,

84
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:59,680
even this humble hope

85
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:00,920
is starting to become...

86
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:01,640
Ms. Su,

87
00:10:02,880 --> 00:10:04,720
do you really have no doubts

88
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:08,400
about your father's death?

89
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,360
What did you say?

90
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,880
Remember our deal.

91
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:16,880
You'll marry Lu Zhen'an,

92
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:19,530
and I'll give you what you want.

93
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:22,800
What do you know?

94
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:27,400
Mr. Su, your father,

95
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:29,440
was a genius.

96
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,840
Unfortunately,

97
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:31,920
his patent

98
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:35,200
harmed the core interests of most people.

99
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:37,600
An engineer with no background

100
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:41,010
was holding a gold mine
big enough to disrupt this industry.

101
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:42,440
Do you think

102
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:47,200
he could keep it?

103
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:52,400
You must have someone
change the technical parameters

104
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:54,320
before Su Minghao's final test.

105
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:55,580
Capital chain.

106
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:57,880
Yes, cut it off.

107
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,320
Make it clean.

108
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:00,680
Give it to me!

109
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:01,800
Who is it?

110
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,200
Is it Lu Zhen'an?

111
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,200
Give me the recorder!

112
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,200
Give me the voice recorder!

113
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,400
What did he do?

114
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:07,520
Give it to me!

115
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:08,520
Give me the recording!

116
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:10,160
Ms. Su, calm down.

117
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:11,480
Calm down!

118
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:14,440
This is all in the past.

119
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:16,120
After all, your father

120
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,760
chose a path of no return.

121
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:21,320
No...

122
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,000
Calm down.

123
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:23,600
He wouldn't.

124
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:27,600
He'd never abandon us!

125
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:30,840
You were the ones who got him killed!

126
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:31,880
It was Lu Zhen'an!

127
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,040
Give it to me!

128
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,560
Give me the voice recorder!

129
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:36,020
I want to know everything!

130
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:37,640
I want the evidence! Give it to me!

131
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:38,560
Ms. Su,

132
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:40,240
you're in the Lu residence.

133
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,680
Keep your voice down.

134
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:42,640
Fine.

135
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,880
If you want all the evidence,

136
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:45,760
you must

137
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:56,560
offer something valuable in exchange.

138
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:00,800
Playing with fish in this courtyard

139
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:02,080
isn't enough.

140
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:06,960
You have to show me your sincerity.

141
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:09,960
Shameless!

142
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:16,720
Ms. Su.

143
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,320
Some secrets

144
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:27,400
require a deeper understanding

145
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:31,240
in a more private place.

146
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:38,120
Ms. Su, it's getting windy.

147
00:12:38,560 --> 00:12:39,720
Don't catch a cold.

148
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,600
Think it through.

149
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:44,920
I'll be waiting for you.

150
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:50,000
Ms. Su.

151
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,120
Roses are beautiful,

152
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:56,280
but they have sharp thorns.

153
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:57,880
If you want to pick them,

154
00:12:58,360 --> 00:13:01,800
we'll both have to pay a price.

155
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:20,120
Don't touch me!

156
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,240
You must give me

157
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:25,480
what I want on the wedding day.

158
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:27,080
Okay.

159
00:13:27,400 --> 00:13:28,800
I won't touch you.

160
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,100
But where's the money?

161
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:33,160
I will give it to you.

162
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:40,240
I bet Lu Zhen'an

163
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,720
never would've imagined

164
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:44,640
that I've already

165
00:13:46,560 --> 00:13:47,880
tasted his woman.
